After Distro install we need

Video server, compositor and drivers
	xorg, xinit, xf86-video -vesa, picom / compton

Common C libraries and package tools for compiling dwm 
	libxft, libx11, libxinerama
	make gcc bc pkg-config
 
For a minimalist system you will need to install fonts:
	terminus-font (others are optional)

Sound drivers:	
	alsa-utils

If you run a virtual machine you will also need:
	linux-headers and virtualbox-guest-utils

Everything else is optionall





